{"tid":1188071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"引渡修例　模糊香港普通法一向原則　中國冇法治唔分清","createTime":"2019-06-06T04:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T04:40:23.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"63245880051c8c9bbb04e1b41ffc4cb52d87d9f1","tid":1188071,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:40:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2435201566715920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2435201566715920&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BguoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=27a621e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2435201566715920</a><br />\n<br />\n香港普通法一向係行dualist view of international law。支那則係認為dualism、monism唔使分得咁清，因為佢哋冇法治。逃犯條例就係模糊呢一點。"}]}